  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introdução a Totem PL Parser</title>

    <para>
      The <application>Totem PL Parser</application> package contains a simple
GObject-based library used to parse multiple playlist formats.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Informação do Pacote</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Transferência (HTTP): <ulink url="&totem-pl-parser-download-http;"/>
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Transferência (FTP): <ulink url="&totem-pl-parser-download-ftp;"/>
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Soma de verificação MD5: &totem-pl-parser-md5sum;
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Tamanho da transferência: &totem-pl-parser-size;
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Espaço em disco estimado exigido: &totem-pl-parser-buildsize;
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Tempo de construção estimado: &totem-pl-parser-time;
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Dependências de Totem PL Parser</bridgehead>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Recomendada</bridgehead>
    <para role="recommended">
      <xref linkend="gobject-introspection"/>, <xref linkend="libarchive"/>, and
<xref linkend="libgcrypt"/>
    </para>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Opcionais</bridgehead>
    <para role="optional">
      <!-- uses it to look for packages -->
<xref linkend="cmake"/>, <xref linkend="gtk-doc"/>, <xref linkend="gvfs"/>
(for some tests), <ulink
url="https://ltp.sourceforge.net/coverage/lcov.php"> LCOV</ulink>, and
<ulink url="https://sourceforge.net/projects/quvi">libquvi &gt;= 0.9.1 and
libquvi-scripts</ulink> - if they are installed, then <ulink
url="https://github.com/diegonehab/luasocket">lua-socket (git)</ulink> is
necessary for the tests
    </para>

    <para condition="html" role="usernotes">Observações de Usuário(a): <ulink url="&blfs-wiki;/totem-pl-parser"/>
    </para>
  </sect2>

  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Instalação de Totem PL Parser</title>

    <para>
      Install <application>Totem PL Parser</application> by running the following
commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>mkdir build &amp;&amp;
cd    build &amp;&amp;

meson --prefix=/usr --buildtype=release .. &amp;&amp;
ninja</userinput></screen>

    <para>
       To test the results, issue: <command>ninja test</command>.
    </para>

    <para>
      Agora, como o(a) usuário(a) <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>ninja install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

